'''Dominique Desseigne''' (born 19 August 1944 in [[Commercy]]) is a [[France|French]] businessperson. He is the chief executive of [[Groupe Lucien Barrière]].<ref>Interview with [[Jean-Pierre Thiollet]], ''France-Soir'', 26 October 2009, http://www.francesoir.fr/actualite/societe/dominique-desseigne-“notre-entreprise-une-affaire-generations”-44572.html{{dead link|date=December 2016 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}.</ref>
